      "title": "Identifying the British Indian Ocean Territory",
      "items": [
        {
          "kind": "centeredImage",
          "imageUrl": "/images/british-indian-ocean-territory/0_summary_io.png"
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/british-indian-ocean-territory/British_Indian_Ocean_Territory_in_United_Kingdom.svg.png",
              "imageLink": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/96/British_Indian_Ocean_Territory_in_United_Kingdom.svg/2560px-British_Indian_Ocean_Territory_in_United_Kingdom.svg.png",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "The British Indian Ocean Territory is an United Kingdom overseas territory in the Indian Ocean. As such, it is counted as **the UK** for country streaks purposes.",
              "Beware that none of the coverage is considered pinpointable, and as a result you are unlikely to get it in most community-made maps. As such, this guide is mainly intended to give a general idea of what type of coverage you can find on the islands."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/british-indian-ocean-territory/io_trekker.png",
              "imageLink": "https://goo.gl/maps/ATdKjiPLx4M99tSD6",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "Coverage was taken with a Generation 3 **trekker**."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/british-indian-ocean-territory/io_coveragemap.png",
              "imageLink": "/images/british-indian-ocean-territory/io_coveragemap.png",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "Coverage is mostly found on small atolls in the northern half of the territory."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/british-indian-ocean-territory/io_beaches.png",
              "imageLink": "https://goo.gl/maps/ijtdCuJsHeLYZ7ns5",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "A large portion of the coverage is taken on sand beaches. You will typically see many palm trees along the beaches."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/british-indian-ocean-territory/io_palmforest.png",
              "imageLink": "https://goo.gl/maps/YV4Hz5ufXvUqKB2R7",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "Coastal palm forests also comprise a significant portion of the coverage. They almost exclusively consist of coconut palms."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/british-indian-ocean-territory/io_mangroves.png",
              "imageLink": "https://goo.gl/maps/VhCDqJM7gF6yuK95A",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "Mangroves can be found on several of the atolls."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/british-indian-ocean-territory/io_fields.png",
              "imageLink": "https://goo.gl/maps/oSskxDoYUHWp1ec49",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "Some of the larger islands with coverage have grassy fields surrounded by bushes and palms."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/british-indian-ocean-territory/io_water.png",
              "imageLink": "https://goo.gl/maps/wcNcrMFAdc5jUbK48",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "The trekker can occasionally be found walking offshore in the water."
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "tip",
      "title": "Spotlight",
      "items": [
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
